# Environment files
# Lovable convention kept: the root .env holds ONLY publishable values (anon
# key, browser Maps key) and stays committed. Anything secret must not go in it.
!.env
!.env.*
!.env.example

# Edge-function secrets (service-role key, Resend, etc.) — NEVER commit.
supabase/functions/.env
backup/
